# ── AI features (alert triage + SAR drafting) ───────────────────────────────
# The Alerts workspace uses Claude through the Vercel AI Gateway. Without a key
# the app runs fine — only the "Generate analysis" / "Draft with AI" actions
# return a friendly "AI is not configured" message.
#
# Get a key: https://vercel.com/d?to=%2F%5Bteam%5D%2F%7E%2Fai-gateway%2Fapi-keys
# On Vercel deployments this is provided automatically via OIDC.
AI_GATEWAY_API_KEY=
